t|08|14th place}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Leonard'''<br><small>The LARPer</small>\n|{{stribe|Xhakum|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}\n|{{Sort|08|13th place}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|''Amy''\n|{{stribe|eniledam|{{nowrap|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}}}\n|''Returned to game''{{efn|Samey was the contestant with the most votes. However, Amy had a reaction to a poisonous apple that Samey gave her, which prevented her from being able to speak. Samey then takes Amy's identity and uses this as a way to stay in the competition. It is because of this that Chris accidentally eliminates Amy under the impression that she is Samey.}} \n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Rodney'''<br><small>The Country Boy</small>\n|{{stribe|eniledam|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}\n|{{sort|08|12th place}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Samey'''<br><small>The Good Twin</small>\n|{{stribe|eniledam|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}\n|{{sort|03|11th/10th place}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Amy'''<br><small>The Evil Twin</small>\n|{{stribe|eniledam|{{nowrap|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}}}\n|{{sort|03|11th/10th place}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Ella'''<br><small>The Fairytale Princess</small>\n|{{stribe|Xhakum|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}\n|{{sort|04|Disqualified{{efn|Despite Wanyihtam Maskwak winning the challenge, Chris disqualified Ella after he found out that she was caught singing by Sugar, which is something Chris refused to allow. Sugar did so by giving Chris an anonymous note.}}<br />9th place}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Topher'''<br><small>The Chris Wannabe</small>\n|{{stribe|eniledam|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}\n|{{stribe|eniledam|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}\n|{{sort|03|8th place}}{{efn|Topher voted for himself because he was tricked into thinking that he would become the new host of the show. However, Chris reveals that it was all a prank, and Topher was instead eliminated from the competition.}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Dave'''<br>The Normal Guy</small>\n|{{stribe|xhakum|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}\n|{{stribe|xhakum|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}\n|rowspan=7 {{stribe|lavita|Merge}}\n|{{sort|03|7th place}}{{efn|Due to being rejected by Sky, Dave decided to vote himself out of the game.}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Scarlett'''<br><small>The Quiet Braniac</small>\n|{{stribe|eniledam|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}\n|{{stribe|eniledam|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}\n|{{sort|6|Disqualified{{efn|Chris disqualified Scarlett for attempting to blow up the island in exchange for the million dollar prize.}}<br />6th/5th place}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Max'''<br><small>The Super Villain</small>\n|{{stribe|eniledam|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}\n|{{stribe|xhakum|{{nowrap|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}}}{{efn|This contestant was originally on Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak, but was switched over to Waneyihtam Maskwak.}} \n|{{sort|6|Disqualified{{efn|Due to not wanting any more evil contestants after Scarlett's plan, Chris disqualified Max for being evil.}}<br />6th/5th place}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Jasmine'''<br><small>The Outback Survivalist</small>\n|{{stribe|eniledam|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}\n|{{stribe|eniledam|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}\n|{{sort|03|4th place}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Sugar'''<br><small>The Pageant Queen</small>\n|{{stribe|xhakum|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}\n|{{stribe|xhakum|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}\n|{{sort|03|3rd place}}\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |'''Sky'''<br><small>The Athlete</small>\n|{{stribe|xhakum|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}\n|{{stribe|eniledam|{{nowrap|Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak}}}}{{efn|This contestant was originally on Waneyihtam Maskwak, but was switched over to Pim\u00e2potew Kinosewak.}}\n|{{sort|18|Winner/runner-up}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|'''Shawn'''<br><small>The Zombie Conspiracy Nut</small>\n|{{stribe|xhakum|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}\n|{{stribe|xhakum|Waneyihtam Maskwak}}\n|{{sort|18|Winner/runner-up}}\n|}\n\n=== Pahkitew Island Cast ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:480px;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:orange\"| Voice actor\n! style=\"background:orange\"| Role\n! style=\"background:orange\"| Episodes worked\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Cl\u00e9 Bennett]]\n|